jobDescription: A super relaxed, enthusiastic hiker, who loves to code
aboutText: I am Aarnav Sanghvi, a Software Developer with a passion for coding. I have extensive experience with ReactJS, AI, and TailwindCSS, and I am constantly learning and pushing the boundaries of what I can do with technology. Outside of coding, I enjoy reading, listening to podcasts, and hiking. I am a super relaxed, enthusiastic hiker, and I bring that same enthusiasm to my work. My background in coding, combined with my extensive experience with AI, ReactJS, and TailwindCSS, make me uniquely qualified to pursue a career in software development.
